Title: Soumya Impex Ever C20 Vitamin C Serum(15 ml)
Description: Vitamin C Serum 20% Ever C20 15ml Key Ingredients : Ethyl Ascorbic Acid Eq. to L- Ascorbic Acid 20% w/v 15ml Bottle Benefits - Ethyl L-ascorbic acid (Ever C20) brightens and tones sun-damaged and dull-looking skin with dark spots as it has multiple inhibition effect in the process of melanogenesis. The 1st is inhibition of tyrosinase activity; the 2nd is Inhibition of polymerization of melanin monomers in the melanogenesis pathway. - Defends the skin against free radicals and environmental damage - Stimulates collagen synthesis and plays an active role in the prevention of premature aging of the skin. - Minimizes the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles - Helps to reduce skin discolourations. - Vitamin C is an excellent free radical scavenger. - Once absorbed into the skin, this water-soluble vitamin can also help regenerate vitamin E that has been oxidized and vitamin E is the most efficient inhibitor of lipid peroxidation in cell membranes. Directions for use - Apply on a thoroughly clean skin. - Dampen skin with water prior to application. - Apply sufficient quantity to cover the affected area and massage gently into skin till it is fully absorbed. - Apply a good broad spectrum sunscreen with at least 20 SPF or more and if necessary, follow with your moisturizer. - Avoid contact with eyes. Precaution For external use only, avoid contact with eyes and mucous membranes. If irritation develops, discontinue use. Consult your physician. Keep out of reach of children. On rare occasions, topical vitamin C can cause some mild dryness or flaking. Counteract this side effect with a good moisturizer. Use within 3 months after opening the bottle."

Title: SENECIO™ 'S 100Pc Mix Rhinestone & 2g Mini Professional Beauty Decorate Tips Nail Art Acrylic Glue(Multicolor)
Description: Nail Glue : Small bottle design,Compact, portable, easy to carry and store. step by step guide for creating a dazzling array of designs in rhinestone nail art Apply base coat, followed by the shade of nail paint you would like to have and let it dry well. Dab a little base coat on the manicure stick and pick the rhinestone with it by sticking it on the top side, with its back not touching the stick. Now, dab a little of base coat on the back side of the rhinestone, making sure that it is not too much. Gently place the rhinestone on your nail and let it set itself by drying. Repeat the steps on all the nails and create the design you want too. Finish up with a top coat so that the stones are sealed on the nails. Precautions : 1).Keep out of reach of children 2).Eye irritant, if eye contact occurs, flush with water, seek medical advice at once 3).Prevent direct contact with skin, if skin bonding occurs, soak in nail polish remover or acetone Can be used on natural nails or false nails. Individually sealed.

Lifestyle-You 9 Sheets Nail Art Stencils SET D(Black)
Description: Instructions for use – Apply a base colour to your nail and let it completely dry, Choose your desired stencil design. Peel it off the backing paper and carefully stick it on your nail. Press it firmly on your nail and make sure there is no air bubble, Now choose the second nail polish shade with which you want to make the designs on the stencil. Carefully apply it all over the stencil. Don’t apply excess. Just enough to cover the whole stencil, Immediately peel off the stencil. Do it carefully so as not to smudge the second layer which you just applied, You can now see the designs on the stencil on your nails. Let it dry completely, You can now also apply a layer of clear top coat to seal the design, Apart from nail polish, you can also use glitter or beads on the stencil. Design it the way you like. There are so many possibilities. You can also view videos on youtube for nail stencils. Instructions are also included with the pack.
